tion entirely,\nso the service permanently disappeared from etcd.\n\nExtract the cleanup into handleKeepAliveClosed and also drop the cached\nlease id and hash so the next heartbeat performs a full Grant+Put and\nthe service recovers within one RegisterInterval.\n\nRegression introduced by #2822; fix is symmetric with the existing\nsynchronous KeepAliveOnce recovery path that propagates\nrpctypes.ErrLeaseNotFound.\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>","verified_at":"2026-04-20T13:55:01Z"}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/micro/go-micro/commits/90f7617facbd1faea5466273b0ec33c535eea73b","html_url":"https://github.com/micro/go-micro/commit/90f7617facbd1faea5466273b0ec33c535eea73b","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/micro/go-micro/commits/90f7617facbd1faea5466273b0ec33c535eea73b/comments","author":{"login":"asim","id":17530,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3NTMw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/17530?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim","html_url":"https://github.com/asim","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"committer":{"login":"web-flow","id":19864447,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5ODY0NDQ3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow","html_url":"https://github.com/web-flow","followers_url":"https://api