mentService{} -> &Comments{}, etc.)\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01GkduEhcrqcG45rdfYh8dAc\n\n* docs: add Micro Chat to website showcase\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01GkduEhcrqcG45rdfYh8dAc\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>","verified_at":"2026-03-07T09:33:19Z"}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/micro/go-micro/commits/9823f6df5cb71bb1974a8514bcbefaca0e2972c6","html_url":"https://github.com/micro/go-micro/commit/9823f6df5cb71bb1974a8514bcbefaca0e2972c6","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/micro/go-micro/commits/9823f6df5cb71bb1974a8514bcbefaca0e2972c6/comments","author":{"login":"asim","id":17530,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3NTMw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/17530?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim","html_url":"https://github.com/asim","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/asim/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"committer":{"login":"web-flow","id":19864447,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5ODY0NDQ3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow","html_url":"https://github.com/web-flow","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github